 best, I play and when I decide to stop playing or when I decide to keep going, I will let you know.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not know, I just try my best every single day, trying to enjoy a thing that I have been enjoying for so much time.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"so much time\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have been suffering a lot of injuries the last two years so if I feel that I am not competitive enough to keep going or physically I am not ready enough to keep going, I will stop and I will let you know.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I mean, I do not think every day about if I am retiring or not.'\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On his defeat to Djokovic, Nadal added: 'Playing against Novak, without creating damage to him and without having the legs of, 20 years ago is, is almost impossible now.'\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999989788648, \"rank\": 1.0211737712148172e-09, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999924967, \"rank\": 7.525125535501068e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"ht